OL,3,CHundreds of security guards go on week-
OL,4,Clong strike over pay
OL,6,FHundreds of security guards at Job
OL,7,FCentres across the region have gone on
OL,8,Fstrike.
OL,10,FThe week-long walkout of workers
OL,11,Facross Yorkshire and the North East
OL,12,Fstarted on Monday 1 July as a pay
OL,13,Fdispute escalates.
OL,15,FThe guards are employed by private
OL,16,Foutsourcing giant G4S.
