OL,3,CHundreds of security guards go on week-
OL,4,Clong strike over pay
OL,6,FThe GMB Union said in a statement:
OL,7,F"The workers do a difficult, dangerous
OL,8,Fjob; and GMB research shows more than
OL,9,F80% regularly suffer abuse, including
OL,10,Fbeing savaged in the neck by dogs,
OL,11,Fpunched, attacked with screwdrivers
OL,12,Fand customers behaving 'like wild
OL,13,Fanimals'".
OL,15,FLast month, picket lines had been put
OL,16,Fin place at Newcastle, Middlesbrough
OL,17,Fand York. They joined 1,400 guards
OL,18,Facross the UK who were taking part in
OL,19,Fthe two-day industrial action.
