OL,6,FHowever, further industrial action was
OL,7,Fconfirmed after pay disputes escalated.
OL,9,FThe GMB Union claims that 90% of the
OL,10,Fguards who are employed by G4S are
OL,11,Fonly earning minimum wage.
OL,13,FG4S says they have offered a pay
OL,14,Fincrease which is both above minimum
OL,15,Fwage and inflation.
OL,17,FEamon O'Hearn, the GMB National
OL,18,FOfficer, said: "It's not rocket
OL,19,Fscience ` if the DWP and G4S want to
OL,20,Fend this dispute, make sure these
OL,21,Fguards are paid enough to live on.
