OL,3,CHundreds of security guards go on week-
OL,4,Clong strike over pay
OL,6,F"G4S has been handed millions by the
OL,7,FGovernment, yet our members can barely
OL,8,Fafford to feed their families. The
OL,9,Fwork they do is hard; they are
OL,10,Fattacked with alarming regularity just
OL,11,Ffor doing their job.
OL,13,F"The least they expect is to be paid a
OL,14,Fproper wage."
OL,16,FSecurity officers will walk out from
OL,17,FMonday 1 July ` Saturday 6 July.
